### Get releases timeline (centered around current deployed version)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/releases

### Get releases with custom count
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/releases?count=10

### Get older releases (paginate backwards)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/releases?cursor=0.1234.0&direction=before

### Get newer releases (paginate forwards)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/releases?cursor=0.1234.0&direction=after
